 WITH CM,APPROVED SECURITIES CASH COMPONENT RETAINED WITH CM,APPROVED SECURITIES NON-CASH COMPONENT RETAINED WITH CM,NON-APPROVED SECURITIES RETAINED WITH CM,VALUE OF NCCL APPROVED COMMODITIES RETAINED WITH CM,OTHER COLLATERALS RETAINED WITH CM,CASH PLACED WITH NCCL,BANK GUARANTEE (BG) PLACED WITH NCCL,FIXED DEPOSIT RECEIPT (FDR) PLACED WITH NCCL,APPROVED SECURITIES CASH COMPONENT PLACED WITH NCCL,APPROVED SECURITIES NON-CASH COMPONENT PLACED WITH NCCL,VALUE OF NCCL APPROVED COMMODITIES PLACED WITH NCCL'   
  
  
